{"tid":1607734,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"紅十字會今日不同地點設急救站　籲勿阻人道救援","createTime":"2019-10-01T03:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T04:47:10.000Z","uid":124663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ffaba30d7f4a2d5ecd214fa151e43c8efb7eefe8","tid":1607734,"uid":124663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:28:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483487-20191001.htm?spTabChangeable=0&amp;fbclid=IwAR2Up2PRQji4Vt41mac5RrgtwhFKRizMKPGlOuUqfYzjkfFW9SSMrH3lTUQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483487-20191001.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0%26fbclid%3DIwAR2Up2PRQji4Vt41mac5RrgtwhFKRizMKPGlOuUqfYzjkfFW9SSMrH3lTUQ&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7Cdf3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=00894256\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483487-20191001.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0%26fbclid%3DIwAR2Up2PRQji4Vt41mac5RrgtwhFKRizMKPGlOuUqfYzjkfFW9SSMrH3lTUQ&h=89eeaa7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483487-20191001.htm?spTabChangeable=0&amp;fbclid=IwAR2Up2PRQji4Vt41mac5RrgtwhFKRizMKPGlOuUqfYzjkfFW9SSMrH3lTUQ</a><br />\n<br />\n香港紅十字會表示，今日會在不同地點設立急救站，為任何有需要人士提供服務，亦繼續提供心理支援服務 。該會又呼籲各方克制，以人道立場尋求解決方法，處理當前問題。<br />\n<br />\n香港紅十字會再次強調，在任何情况下，各方應優先考慮受影響人士的醫療需要，所有救援人員及車輛應受到尊重及保護，任何阻撓人道救援工作的行為都是不恰當。他們強調，紅十字會一直堅守國際紅十字基本原則，救助有需要人士為首要考慮，不受有關背景或政治立場影響。<br />\n<br />\n香港紅十字會員工及義工提供急救服務，會穿上紅色反光背心、配上印有綠底白十字急救標誌的急救包，背心及急救包上均印有中、英文「香港紅十字會」字樣，背心前方右側的透明窗口，會展示職員或義工證。"},{"pid":"aba2ed35ce11b2525df3fd2581b34953dac918ca","tid":1607734,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:48:18.000Z","msg":"已cut捐款，之前有冇幫過手？"},{"pid":"1764653b968baf3823aa1457aacac93ab1184b11","tid":1607734,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aba2ed35ce11b2525df3fd2581b34953dac918ca","tid":1607734,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:48:18.000Z","msg":"已cut捐款，之前有冇幫過手？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:19:51.000Z","msg":"無，一次都無"},{"pid":"1c2d99eb79f48efe99a02382b497a327fd544b56","tid":1607734,"uid":60287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:21:15.000Z","msg":"唔好信佢地，見到屌柒佢地就得"},{"pid":"16e5577f33c3958dd5111607080d6498fe3b0e34","tid":1607734,"uid":76854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/d/da/Ve4v9v.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20091115115055\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fd%2Fda%2FVe4v9v.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20091115115055&h=b180f719&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"720b49ca58cb8b6975721cb0401685804b9be59e","tid":1607734,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:26:43.000Z","msg":"唔好等香港人死撚哂再出嚟，屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b59881dde1e1e13a81ffd96085120b23edffc7c5","tid":1607734,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:27:41.000Z","msg":"大家夢遊前記得set Telegram 預設訊息<br />\n必要時可救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCXiwqP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCXiwqP.png&h=5c04cb99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPush"},{"pid":"40facb3b695fe7a088c6f30aa5d25ed41fdcc487","tid":1607734,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:47:10.000Z","msg":"遲好過無<br />\n觀察下先"}]}